    "Once there is agreement on the coding scheme then it can be applied to the remaining documents, completing the coding stage of the process as it plays out in the inductive mode.",
    "In the deductive mode, on the other hand, a framework including a set of specific coding categories is already given.",
    "In this case, the job of the qualitative researcher is to classify each quote in each document into one (or more) categories.",
    "Coders must collaborate with one another to develop a shared understanding of precisely how the terms of the framework apply in the specific context under study.",
    "Various techniques were used to enhance the trustworthiness of the analysis."
  ],
